<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <title>GitArchiver🐈‍⬛</title>
</head>

<body>
    {{!-- Cabeçalho --}}
    <div class="container text-light text-center mt-3">
        <h1 class="fs-1">
            Cansado de ficar arquivando aqueles projetos antigos?😩
        </h1>
        <h1 class="fs-2">
            Cansado de ficar copiando sua URL para deletar seus reps?🤬
        </h1>
        <h1 class="fs-3">
            Bem, diga adeus ao complexo, e aceite a simplicidade😁
        </h1>
        <h6>Feito com tempo, e de madrugada, por @Kazbonfim</h6>
    </div>
    {{!-- Formulário de envio --}}
    <div class="container bg-light shadow mt-4 p-4 border border-dark-subtle rounded" style="width: 30rem;">

        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-dark-subtle mb-3"><i>Preenche aqui, papai😎</i></h2>
            <small class="mx-auto"><b>~ Mano Deyvin</b>, antes do grande <b>Rollback</b></small>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <form id="archiveForm">
            <div class="form-floating border mb-3">
                <input name="user" type="text" class="form-control" id="user" placeholder="name@example.com">
                <label for="user">Nome de Usuário na outra rede?</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-floating border">
                <input name="token" type="text" class="form-control" id="token" placeholder="Password">
                <label for="token">Palavra secreta pra entrar pelos fundos?</label>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center my-2">
                <button id="submitBtn" type="submit" class="shadow btn btn-success btn-lg">Arquivar</button>
            </div>
        </form>


        {{!-- Utils --}}
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="../javascripts/axiosPatchExample.js" defer></script>
</body>

</html>